## In Scope:
- Road construction 45 km (paved)  
- One major bridge (foundation, superstructure)  
- Drainage works (culverts, side drains)  
- Road furniture & signage  
- QA/QC tests and lab work  
- Environmental & social safeguards implementation  
- Maintenance period supervision

## Out of Scope:
- Property acquisition outside defined right-of-way  
- Utilities relocation outside the project alignment  
- Major urban works beyond design  

## Deliverables:
- Fully constructed 45 km road  
- Completed bridge  
- QA/QC reports  
- Weekly & milestone reports
